{"tid":1449631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 重整旗鼓!","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:28.000Z","uid":174541,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ce89de705c650734e93cf1acbfef0df08a8ca4a4","tid":1449631,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"人地做開marketing，寫埋本教科書教你跟住做文宣! 成個月咩進步都冇，重係散修修同溫層自high咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記撚住啊!有啲仆街聽到義士爆眼係會拍手叫好。我地再賣血賣肉都喚唔醒班仆街架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">憤怒過後要冷靜面對</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣嘅諗清楚我地係target緊咩人，要點遊說!</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">前線嘅諗清楚每個行為背後有咩用！淨低嘅交俾我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n【藍絲攻略 - 拆解 18 種建制】- 徐緣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179283162169650/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F347912661973385%2Fposts%2F2179283162169650%2F&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e024cc64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179283162169650/</a>"},{"pid":"87715019efe2675ca5d23e94dfd4d7441ea1e7e0","tid":1449631,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"df90e9b3bb781f1159dcc52904e30f45724961a6","tid":1449631,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e51fe18449543770077d44b659ba1624d36d157","tid":1449631,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hk