員：<br />\n<br />\n我係前缐急救員，經過呢幾日我見到警察明顯轉變：<br />\n<br />\n1. 潛伏喺示威者裏便嘅臥底開始出現。當你轉區，佢哋好快就會知道。<br />\n2. 開始減少使用催淚彈，注重物理攻擊和拘捕。<br />\n3. 行動速度比以前快不再對恃。<br />\n<br />\n我有諗過下列嘅解決方法：<br />\n<br />\n1. 不再be water , be 街坊，唔使不停走來走去，自己各區街坊努力參與。因為街坊熟路亦都唔需要搭地鐵去其他佢唔會俾人封死出口，而呢一個方法對急救來講亦都係一件比較好嘅分配，唔使再揹gear同物資周街行。<br />\n2. Be 街坊要每區合作，e.g 深水埗出手，警察來，附近區嘅街坊就要出手，深水埗首先散左先，但係留返係自己屋企，到其他區警察出嚟，深水埗又再聚。區內be water .<br />\n3. 和理非要快啲進行多啲不合作運動同埋罷工罷課。打擊到佢經濟佢先會肉痛。<br />\n4. 罷工唔可以只係一日最少都三日啦。<br />\n5. 大家快啲將美金有銀行都攞出黎擺去其他離岸戶口"},{"pid":"090b5c820341fce69c5e030cf56788a3170f11f2","tid":1449631,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cb77f829d1602451735d5aa79d7f45edf68ffd","tid":1449631,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"文宣圖 裡面冇嘅可以自己upload上去<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F0%2Ffolders%2F1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=b110c1f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt</a>"},{"pid":"f926c8bd212b2fdf32a48ea8e6eb7bcf9cd57869","tid":1449631,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5064630334537a503d70a896954494ffcc229a","tid":1449631,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"【文宣戰線】香港首家長輩Youtube頻道上線啦！〔2〕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440488</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"70afa3b7c471619978c8f0d9eff69b655c3709c8","tid":1449631,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p